ERIC WEINER: --cafe, yes.

01:06:59.750 --> 01:07:00.620
But--

01:07:00.620 --> 01:07:01.340
MIKE NELSON: The coffee house.

01:07:01.340 --> 01:07:03.173
ERIC WEINER: --not
