01:08:15.460 --> 01:08:19.300
is finding these obscure
books, these geniuses, right,

01:08:19.300 --> 01:08:21.720
and borrowing their ideas.

01:08:21.720 --> 01:08:23.670
But crediting them.

01:08:23.670 --> 01:08:26.550
And that had so
much on the habits

01:08:26.550 --> 01:08:30.200
of these particular geniuses.

